{"tid":1614134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"急!!有冇消息? 10.1除左健仔手足 仲有兩個人係危殆!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:00:18.000Z","uid":99478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"92ec48d5b8ec657279d21c85ef6652be3a922d53","tid":1614134,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:54:53.000Z","msg":"求各大傳媒醫護follow-up <br />\n<br />\n醫管局稱，截至今早10時，全港12間公立醫院共接收104名傷者，分別是81男23女，年齡介乎11至75歲。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現時兩名男子危殆，留醫東區醫院及律敦治醫院</span></strong></span>；兩名男子嚴重；29人情況穩定或滿意（當中一人為曾志健），71人經治理後出院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60107233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60107233&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7HljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=2759f5f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60107233&h=e4c03bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60107233</a>"},{"pid":"ca5af5ac7990e994f7dbfa7210cdf5059b780f7d","tid":1614134,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"70ac62502b1baa91ce07c7e717c76ed0c250bccc","tid":1614134,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"8175a8574e94370c0287cb4e388af732ca0ddbca","tid":1614134,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"2/10 有冇人知咩事"},{"pid":"982e06f1eec25d345c4e26b548e263afe82350e5","tid":1614134,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><